
1.Download dls_serial_sim-1.18.tgz at http://controls.diamond.ac.uk/downloads/python/dls_serial_sim/
2.Installation : over Python 2.4 and python-setuptools with root
3.$>tar xvfz dls_serial_sim-1.18.tgz
4.$>cd dls_serial_sim-1.18
5.$dls_serial_sim-1.18>python setup.py install 

or

5.$dls_serial_sim-1.18>vi Makefile
comment out and modifying.
#PYTHON = dls-python
PYTHON = python2.7

